<span class="line"><span style="color:#E1E4E8;">  </span><span style="color:#79B8FF;">&quot;type&quot;</span><span style="color:#E1E4E8;">: </span><span style="color:#9ECBFF;">&quot;module&quot;</span><span style="color:#E1E4E8;">, </span><span style="color:#6A737D;">// 注意，此处设置之后，项目中依赖的引入方式必须遵循ESM规范。</span></span>
